### Get all persons
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons

###

### Get info
GET http://localhost:3001/info

###

### Get person by ID (exists)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons/1

###

### Get person by ID (does not exist)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons/999999

###

### Add a new person
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "number": "555-123456"
}

###

### Add another person
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "number": "555-654321"
}

###

### Error: Missing name
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "123-456789"
}

###

### Error: Missing number
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Missing Number"
}

###

### Error: Duplicate name
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Arto Hellas",
  "number": "999-999999"
}

###

### Delete person (change the ID if needed)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/persons/1

###

### Verify deletion
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons/1

###

### Get all persons after deletion
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons

###

### Unknown endpoint
GET http://localhost:3001/api/unknown